# Docker Deployment Rules

- Use exec form for CMD instructions to ensure proper signal handling
- Implement proper WORKDIR structure
- Copy dependency files before application code
- Use appropriate base images for different stages
- Configure environment variables consistently
- Implement proper startup and shutdown handling
- Set up proper container networking
- Configure appropriate resource limits
- Use Docker Compose for local development
- Implement proper volume management
